---
// 延伸閱讀等區塊用的部落格式卡片（漸層封面＋標題＋描述＋日期＋群集標籤）。
// 傳入 lang 與要精選的 slug 陣列；自動從內容集合抓真實 title/description/date/cluster，
// 只顯示已發布（date_published <= 今天）且存在的文章，未到期或不存在的自動略過。
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';

interface Props {
  lang: 'zh-hant' | 'zh-hans' | 'en';
  slugs: string[];
}
const { lang, slugs } = Astro.props;

const now = new Date();
const all = await getCollection(
  'blog',
  (p) => p.id.startsWith(`${lang}/`) && !p.data.draft && p.data.date_published <= now
);
const bySlug = new Map(all.map((p) => [p.id.split('/').slice(1).join('/'), p]));
const posts = slugs.map((s) => bySlug.get(s)).filter((p): p is NonNullable<typeof p> => Boolean(p));
const fmt = (d: Date) => d.toISOString().slice(0, 10);

// 與部落格列表頁同一套群集配色（刻意避開橘色＝CTA 專用）
const CLUSTER_STYLE: Record<string, { short: string; g1: string; g2: string }> = {
  '1': { short: 'GEO', g1: '#1d3a8a', g2: '#4f8cff' },
  '2': { short: 'AI 產線', g1: '#0e5b56', g2: '#2dd4bf' },
  '3': { short: 'On-page', g1: '#14532d', g2: '#4ade80' },
  '4': { short: 'Off-page', g1: '#701a4b', g2: '#f472b6' },
  '5': { short: '多語言', g1: '#4c1d95', g2: '#a78bfa' },
  '6': { short: 'AIO', g1: '#155e75', g2: '#22d3ee' },
};
// zh-hant/zh-hans cluster 值含「群集 N」；en 值是純標籤（GEO / AIO / On-page SEO…），逐一比對。
function clusterOf(c?: string) {
  const num = c?.match(/群集\s*(\d)/)?.[1];
  if (num && CLUSTER_STYLE[num]) return CLUSTER_STYLE[num];
  const s = (c || '').toLowerCase();
  if (/aio/.test(s)) return CLUSTER_STYLE['6'];
  if (/on-page/.test(s)) return CLUSTER_STYLE['3'];
  if (/off-page/.test(s)) return CLUSTER_STYLE['4'];
  if (/multilingual/.test(s)) return CLUSTER_STYLE['5'];
  if (/ai content/.test(s)) return CLUSTER_STYLE['2'];
  if (/geo/.test(s)) return CLUSTER_STYLE['1'];
  return { short: 'SEO', g1: '#2a313c', g2: '#5b6675' };
}
---
{posts.length > 0 && (
  <div class="rcards">
    {posts.map((p) => {
      const c = clusterOf(p.data.cluster);
      const slug = p.id.split('/').slice(1).join('/');
      return (
        <a class="rcard" href={`/${lang}/blog/${slug}/`}>
          <div class="rcover">
            <img class="rcover-img" src={c.short === 'AIO' ? '/og/base-aio.png' : '/og/base-geo.png'} alt="" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="rbrand">GeoSeoToday</span>
            <span class="rtitle">{p.data.title}</span>
            <span class="rtag">{c.short}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rbody">
            <p class="rdesc">{p.data.description}</p>
            <p class="rmeta">{fmt(p.data.date_published)}</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      );
    })}
  </div>
)}

<style>
  .rcards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(210px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 10px 0 8px;
  }
  .rcard {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-decoration: none;
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden; transition: transform .18s, border-color .18s;
  }
  .rcard:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .rcover {
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 8; position: relative; padding: 14px 16px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    background: #0e1116; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .rcover-img { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; z-index: 0; }
  .rcover::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(14,17,22,.9) 0%, rgba(14,17,22,.55) 52%, rgba(14,17,22,.15) 100%);
  }
  .rbrand {
    position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 16px; z-index: 2;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); letter-spacing: .4px;
  }
  .rtitle {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.45;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
    display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 3; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .rtag {
    position: absolute; bottom: 12px; right: 16px; z-index: 2;
    font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,255,.9);
    background: rgba(0,0,0,.35); padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 99px;
  }
  .rbody { padding: 14px 16px 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; flex: 1; }
  .rdesc {
    margin: 0; color: var(--dim); font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.6;
    display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .rmeta { margin: auto 0 0; color: var(--dim); font-size: 12px; opacity: .75; }
</style>
